comment: Collison (SAC) legally contests Rose's (CHI) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Cousins (SAC) and Gasol (CHI) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Gasol (CHI) is in the lane for more than three seconds.
Dunleavy (CHI) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Belinelli (SAC) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Gasol (CHI) and Cousins (SAC) engage and separate under the rim on the long rebound.
Rondo (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that possession be awarded to CHI was upheld.
Butler (CHI) and Rondo (SAC) briefly engage on the inbound.
Gibson (CHI) continues moving as he sets the screen on Belinelli (SAC) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Gasol (CHI) was in front of the three-point line on his made field goal was upheld.
Belinelli (SAC) and Dunleavy (CHI) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Cousins (SAC) and Dunleavy (CHI) make foot contact that causes Dunleavy to lose his balance.
Gasol (CHI) sets the screen on Rondo (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
